<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>비밀번호 변경</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,typography"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet"/>
<script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#6366F1", // Indigo 500
            "background-light": "#F9FAFB", // Gray 50
            "background-dark": "#1F2937", // Gray 800
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ["Noto Sans KR", "sans-serif"],
          },
          borderRadius: {
            DEFAULT: "0.5rem", // 8px
          },
        },
      },
    };
  </script>
<style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display">
<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4">
<header class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center p-4 absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">홈 버튼</a>
<a class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">MY</a>
</header>
<main class="w-full max-w-md bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
<h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">비밀번호 변경</h1>
<form class="space-y-6">
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2" for="current-password">현재 비밀번호 입력</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary" id="current-password" name="current-password" placeholder="현재 비밀번호를 입력하세요" type="password"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2" for="new-password">새로운 비밀번호 입력</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary" id="new-password" name="new-password" placeholder="새로운 비밀번호를 입력하세요" type="password"/>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2" for="confirm-password">새로운 비밀번호 재입력</label>
<div class="relative">
<input class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-md border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:ring-primary focus:border-primary" id="confirm-password" name="confirm-password" placeholder="새로운 비밀번호를 다시 입력하세요" type="password"/>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-500 dark:text-red-400" id="password-match-status" style="display: none;">비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.</p>
<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" id="password-match-success" style="display: none;">비밀번호가 일치합니다.</p>
</div>
</div>
<button class="w-full bg-primary text-white font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-indigo-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900 transition-colors" type="submit">
          확인
        </button>
</form>
</main>
</div>
<script>
    const newPassword = document.getElementById('new-password');
    const confirmPassword = document.getElementById('confirm-password');
    const matchStatus = document.getElementById('password-match-status');
    const matchSuccess = document.getElementById('password-match-success');
    function checkPasswordMatch() {
        if (newPassword.value === '' && confirmPassword.value === '') {
            matchStatus.style.display = 'none';
            matchSuccess.style.display = 'none';
            return;
        }
        if (newPassword.value === confirmPassword.value) {
            matchStatus.style.display = 'none';
            if (confirmPassword.value) {
                matchSuccess.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                matchSuccess.style.display = 'none';
            }
            confirmPassword.classList.remove('border-red-500', 'dark:border-red-400');
            confirmPassword.classList.add('border-green-500', 'dark:border-green-400');
        } else {
            matchStatus.style.display = 'block';
            matchSuccess.style.display = 'none';
            confirmPassword.classList.add('border-red-500', 'dark:border-red-400');
            confirmPassword.classList.remove('border-green-500', 'dark:border-green-400');
        }
    }
    newPassword.addEventListener('input', checkPasswordMatch);
    confirmPassword.addEventListener('input', checkPasswordMatch);
  </script>

</body></html>